Input: synaptics-rmi4 - convert irq distribution to irq_domain

Convert the RMI driver to use the standard mechanism for
distributing IRQs to the various functions.

Tested on:
* S7300 (F11, F34, F54)
* S7817 (F12, F34, F54)

